dungeonDesc.cn: <@ct.key>洁尔佩塔是兼具法术和物理能力的辅助干员。她可以在触发法术异常后快速造成击飞，并且施放终结技后可以对大范围内的敌人施加法术脆弱效果。</>
dungeonDesc.en: <@ct.key>Gilberta is a supporter with both Arts and Physical abilities. She can quickly Lift enemies after triggering Arts Reactions. Once cast, her ultimate also applies Arts Susceptibility to enemies within a large area.</>

dungeonDesc.cn: 洁尔佩塔是兼具法术和物理能力的辅助干员。她可以在触发法术异常后快速造成击飞，并且施放终结技后可以对大范围内的敌人施加法术脆弱效果。

dungeonDesc.en: <@ct.key>Ardelia is a supporter with outstanding HP treatment skills. Her battle skill and combo skill make enemies take more DMG, while her battle skill and ultimate can heal teammates.</>

dungeonDesc.cn: <@ct.key>昼雪能保护队友反击敌人，对受伤的队友进行治疗，同时还可以通过终结技冻结敌人。</>
dungeonDesc.en: <@ct.key>Snowshine can protect teammates by retaliating enemy attacks, provide HP treatment to injured teammates, and cast ultimates that can apply Solidification to the enemy.</>

dungeonDesc.cn: <@ct.key>艾维文娜拥有特殊的攻击方式，她可以投掷“雷枪”，并通过战技将所有“雷枪”一次性收回，从而造成大量电磁伤害。</>
dungeonDesc.en: <@ct.key>Avywenna has a unique way to attack her enemies. She can throw Thunderlances into the battlefield and use her battle skill to retrieve all thrown lances at once, dealing massive Electric DMG at one go.</>

dungeonDesc.cn: <@ct.key>余烬是一名重装干员。她可以在主控受伤后攻击目标，同时治疗主控。同时还能使用终结技为全体队友施加护盾。</>
dungeonDesc.en: <@ct.key>Ember is a defender who attacks a target hitting the controlled operator while giving HP treatment to the latter. Her ultimate also grants a Shield to every teammate.</>

featureDesc.en:
<@bl.key>Item Control Ports</> display the icon of the item that they <@bl.key>allow to pass through</>.
Use the icon to determine the type of items that can be moved along a <@bl.key>transport belt</> with the <@bl.key>Item Control Port</>.

mainGoalDesc.cn:
改变物品准入口的物品限制，使源矿顺利进入精炼炉生产 
改变物品准入口的数量限制，使源矿顺利进入精炼炉生产
mainGoalDesc.en:
Change the item restrictions of the Item Control Port to let Originium Ore enter the Refining Unit for processing 
Change the quantity restrictions of the Item Control Port to let Originium Ore enter the Refining Unit for processing

dungeonDesc.cn: 集成工业系统现已引入物流桥，可通过传送带的跨接进行更为灵活的物流运输。
dungeonDesc.en: The AIC Factory can now utilize the Belt Bridge that lets a transport belt span another.

extraGoalDesc.cn: 使用物流桥，为3台热能池提供源矿
extraGoalDesc.en: Use the Belt Bridge to supply 3 Thermal Banks with Originium Ore

featureDesc.cn: <@bl.key>物流桥</>可使两条交叉的传送带各自进行传输而互不影响。
featureDesc.en: The <@bl.key>Belt Bridge</> allows a transport belt to cross over another without interfering the product flows of both.

mainGoalDesc.cn: 使用物流桥，将源矿输入粉碎机中
mainGoalDesc.en: Use the Belt Bridge to deliver Originium Ore into the Shredding Unit

dungeonDesc.cn: 集成工业系统现已引入汇流器，可将多条传送带进行合并到一起，以简化物流运输。
dungeonDesc.en: The AIC Factory can now utilize the Converger that converges product flows of multiple transport belts into a single belt.

extraGoalDesc.cn: 使用汇流器，将优质荞愈胶囊、优质柑实罐头和低容谷地电池合流存入仓库
extraGoalDesc.en: Use the Converger to merge the Buck Capsule [B] line, Canned Citrome [B] line, and LC Valley Battery line into a single transport belt to store them all in the Depot

featureDesc.cn: <@bl.key>汇流器</>可将最多3条传送带并入1条传送带进行传输。
featureDesc.en: The <@bl.key>Converger</> can merge up to 3 belts into 1 belt to combine product flows.

mainGoalDesc.cn: 使用汇流器，将荞愈胶囊和柑实罐头合流存入仓库
mainGoalDesc.en: Use the Converger to merge the Buck Capsule [C] line and Canned Citrome [C] line into a single line to store both products in the Depot

dungeonDesc.cn: 拆解机可以将灌装液体重新拆解为液体和空瓶子。请使用拆解机重构芽针针剂生产线。
dungeonDesc.en: The Separating Unit can separate a filled container into the fluid content and the empty container. Use the Separating Unit to complete the Yazhen Syringe [C] production line.

extraGoalDesc.cn: 将锦草溶液重新灌装进紫晶质瓶中并存入仓库
extraGoalDesc.en: Fill the empty Amethyst Bottles with Jincao Solution and store the products in the Depot

featureDesc.cn:
<@bl.key>拆解机</>可以对物品进行物理拆分，比如将灌有液体的瓶子拆分为空瓶子和液体。
将灌有锦草溶液的蓝铁瓶输送到<@bl.key>拆解机</>中进行拆分，获得空的蓝铁瓶。
将灌有芽针溶液的紫晶质瓶放入<@bl.key>拆解机</>中进行拆分，获得芽针溶液。
将获得的空蓝铁瓶和芽针溶液输送到<@bl.key>灌装机</>中重新灌装，获得灌有芽针溶液的蓝铁瓶，可用于生产芽针针剂。
featureDesc.en:
<@bl.key>Separating Units</> can physically separate certain items. An example would be separating a bottled fluid into an empty bottle and the fluid contents. 
Move Jincao Solution in Ferrium Bottles into the <@bl.key>Separating Unit</> to get empty Ferrium Bottles. 
Move Yazhen Solution in Amethyst Bottles into the <@bl.key>Separating Unit</> to get Yazhen Solution. 
Finally, move Yazhen Solution and empty Ferrium Bottles to the <@bl.key>Filling Unit</> for refilling and produce Yazhen Syringe [C].

mainGoalDesc.cn:
使用拆解机拆分灌有芽针溶液的紫晶质瓶，获得芽针溶液
使用拆解机拆分灌有锦草溶液的蓝铁瓶，获得空蓝铁瓶
完善产线并生产芽针针剂
mainGoalDesc.en:
Use the Separating Unit to separate the Yazhen Solution in Amethyst Bottles 
Use the Separating Unit to separate Jincao Solution in Ferrium Bottles 
Complete the Yazhen Syringe [C] production line

dungeonDesc.cn: 请使用灌装机搭建药品和食品的自动化生产线。
dungeonDesc.en: Use the Filling Unit to set up auto-production lines for food and medicine.

featureDesc.cn:
将荞花粉末和紫晶质瓶放入<@bl.key>灌装机</>中可生产荞愈胶囊。
将柑实粉末和紫晶质瓶放入<@bl.key>灌装机</>中可生产柑实罐头。
featureDesc.en:
Place Buckflower Powder and Amethyst Bottles in the <@bl.key>Filling Unit</> to produce Buck Capsule [C]. 
Place Citrome Powder and Amethyst Bottles in the <@bl.key>Filling Unit</> to produce Canned Citrome [C].

mainGoalDesc.cn:
生产荞愈胶囊并存入仓库
生产柑实罐头并存入仓库
mainGoalDesc.en:
Produce Buck Capsule [C] and store it in the Depot 
Produce Canned Citrome [C] and store it in the Depot

dungeonDesc.cn: 请使用集成工业系统对蓝铁矿进行进一步加工，并使用蓝铁瓶生产更优质的柑实罐头。
dungeonDesc.en: Use the AIC Factory to process Ferrium Ore. Use Ferrium Bottles to produce improved canned citromes.

extraGoalDesc.cn: 生产2份优质柑实罐头
extraGoalDesc.en: Produce Canned Citrome [B]×2

featureDesc.cn:
使用<@bl.key>蓝铁矿</>替换原本食品生产线中<@bl.key>紫晶矿</>，可罐装更优质的食品。
将蓝铁矿输入到<@bl.key>精炼炉</>中可生产蓝铁块。
将蓝铁块输入到<@bl.key>塑形机</>中可生产蓝铁瓶。
将蓝铁瓶和柑实粉末输入到<@bl.key>灌装机</>中可生产<@bl.key>优质柑实罐头</>。
featureDesc.en:
Replace <@bl.key>Amethyst Ore</> of the existing food production line with <@bl.key>Ferrium Ore</> to produce higher quality canned food. 
Transport Ferrium Ore into the <@bl.key>Refining Unit</> to produce Ferrium. 
Transport Ferrium into the <@bl.key>Moulding Unit</> to produce Ferrium Bottles. 
Transport Ferrium Bottles and Citrome Powder into the <@bl.key>Filling Unit</> to produce <@bl.key>Canned Citrome [B]</>.

mainGoalDesc.cn: 生产1份优质柑实罐头
mainGoalDesc.en: Produce Canned Citrome [B]×1

dungeonDesc.cn: 请使用研磨机更新药剂产线，生产恢复效果更佳的精选荞愈胶囊。
dungeonDesc.en: Upgrade the medicine production line with the Grinding Unit to produce the improved medicine: Buck Capsule [A].

extraGoalDesc.cn: 挑战用更少的供电桩来维持运转
extraGoalDesc.en: Use as few Electric Pylons as possible and keep the production line running.

featureDesc.cn:
将荞花粉末和砂叶粉末输入到<@bl.key>研磨机</>中可生产<@bl.key>细磨荞花粉末</>。
将钢质瓶和细磨荞花粉末输入到<@bl.key>灌装机</>中可生产<@bl.key>精选荞愈胶囊</>。
featureDesc.en:
Place Buckflower Powder and Sandleaf Powder into the <@bl.key>Grinding Unit</> to produce <@bl.key>Ground Buckflower Powder</>. 
Place Steel Bottle and Ground Buckflower Powder into the <@bl.key>Filling Unit</> to produce <@bl.key>Buck Capsule [A]</>.

mainGoalDesc.cn: 生产1份精选荞愈胶囊
mainGoalDesc.en: Produce Buck Capsule [A]×1

dungeonDesc.cn: 运用管道和灌装机的液体模式，将液体输入到设备中以进行武陵地区的食品和药品生产。
dungeonDesc.en: Use pipes and Filling Unit Fluid Mode to transport fluids into the facility to produce Wuling food and medicine.

extraGoalDesc.cn: 使用封装机生产芽针针剂
extraGoalDesc.en: Use the Packaging Unit to produce Yazhen Syringe [C]

featureDesc.cn:
将植物粉末和清水输入到<@bl.key>反应池</>中混合可以生产植物溶液。
将铁制零件和装有锦草溶液的蓝铁瓶输入到<@bl.key>封装机</>中可生产锦草软饮。
将铁制零件和装有芽针溶液的蓝铁瓶输入到<@bl.key>封装机</>中可生产芽针针剂。
featureDesc.en:
Deliver powdered plant material and Clean Water into the <@bl.key>Reactor Crucible</> and mix them to get a plant solution. 
Deliver Ferrium Parts and Jincao Solution in Ferrium Bottles to the <@bl.key>Packaging Unit</> to produce Jincao Drink.
Deliver Ferrium Parts and Yazhen Solution in Ferrium Bottles to the <@bl.key>Packaging Unit</> to produce Yazhen Syringe [C].

mainGoalDesc.cn:
使用反应池生产锦草溶液
使用封装机生产锦草软饮
mainGoalDesc.en:
Use the Reactor Crucible to produce Jincao Solution 
Use the Packaging Unit to produce Jincao Drink

dungeonDesc.cn: 现需将一批原料加工为粉末，再运回仓库。请使用传送带在现有布局下进行物流连线。
dungeonDesc.en: You must powder a batch of materials and transport the products back to the Depot. Connect the current facilities with transport belts to create a production line.

extraGoalDesc.cn: 只放置1台供电桩为粉碎机、精炼炉和目标储物箱供电
extraGoalDesc.en: Place only 1 Electric Pylon to power the Shredding Unit, Refining Unit, and the target Stash

featureDesc.cn:
使用<@bl.key>传送带</>建立将原料送到生产设备再将产物送回仓库的自动化生产线。
将源矿输送到<@bl.key>精炼炉</>中以产出晶体外壳
将晶体外壳输送到<@bl.key>粉碎机</>中以产出晶体外壳粉末。
featureDesc.en:
Use <@bl.key>transport belts</> to set up an automated production line that delivers raw materials to the processing unit and then moves the products to the Depot. 
Move Originium Ore to the <@bl.key>Refining Unit</> to produce Origocrust. 
Move Origocrust to the <@bl.key>Shredding Unit</> to produce Origocrust Powder.

mainGoalDesc.cn:
使用粉碎机生产3份荞花粉末并存入仓库
使用粉碎机生产3份晶体外壳粉末并存入仓库
mainGoalDesc.en:
Use the Shredding Unit to produce Buckflower Powder×3 and store the products in the Depot 
Use the Shredding Unit to produce Origocrust Powder×3 and store the products in the Depot

dungeonDesc.cn: 请使用集成工业系统搭建荞花粉末的自动化生产线。
dungeonDesc.en: Use the AIC Factory to create an automated Buckflower Powder production line.

extraGoalDesc.cn: 在仓库储备一批晶体外壳粉末
extraGoalDesc.en: Store some Origocrust Powder in the Depot

featureDesc.cn:
<@bl.key>协议核心取货口</>可将物品从仓库持续输出到传送带上。
使用传送带连接设备的输出口到<@bl.key>协议核心输入口</>可将产物运回仓库。
将荞花输送到<@bl.key>粉碎机</>中可生产<@bl.key>荞花粉末</>。
featureDesc.en:
The <@bl.key>PAC Output Port</> can continuously unload items from the Depot to the transport belt. 
Connect a facility output port to a <@bl.key>PAC Input Port</> with a transport line to move facility products to the Depot. 
Deliver Buckflower to the <@bl.key>Shredding Unit</> to produce <@bl.key>Buckflower Powder</>.

mainGoalDesc.cn:
使用粉碎机生产荞花粉末
使用传送带将产出的荞花粉末运回仓库
mainGoalDesc.en:
Use the Shredding Unit to produce Buckflower Powder
Use the transport belt to move the products to the Depot

dungeonDesc.cn: 请使用电驱矿机开采紫晶矿，并将开采到的紫晶矿加工为紫晶纤维。
dungeonDesc.en: Mine Amethyst Ore with Electric Mining Rigs, then process the Amethyst Ore into Amethyst Fiber.

featureDesc.cn:
<@bl.key>电驱矿机</>可以用来开采源矿和紫晶矿。
使用<@bl.key>供电桩</>可为<@bl.key>电驱矿机</>供电。
从<@bl.key>中继器</>运输电力到<@bl.key>供电桩</>可将其接入电网。
featureDesc.en:
<@bl.key>Electric Mining Rigs</> can mine Originium Ore and Amethyst Ore. 
Use <@bl.key>Electric Pylons</> to power the <@bl.key>Electric Mining Rigs</>. 
Transmit power from a <@bl.key>Relay Tower</> and plug the power cable into the <@bl.key>Electric Pylon</> to connect it to the power grid.

mainGoalDesc.cn:
让3台电驱矿机正常运转
将开采到的紫晶矿加工为紫晶纤维
mainGoalDesc.en:
Make 3 Electric Mining Rigs operational 
Process the mined Amethyst Ore into Amethyst Fiber

dungeonDesc.cn: 请合理利用二型电驱矿机，对矿物区所有矿点进行开采。
dungeonDesc.en: Use Electric Mining Rigs Mk II to mine every mining spot of the area.

extraGoalDesc.cn: 开采8个矿点
extraGoalDesc.en: Mine 8 mining spots

featureDesc.cn:
<@bl.key>电驱矿机</>可以用来开采源矿和紫晶矿。
<@bl.key>二型电驱矿机</>可以用来开采源矿、紫晶矿和蓝铁矿。
featureDesc.en:
<@bl.key>Electric Mining Rigs</> can mine Originium Ore and Amethyst Ore. 
<@bl.key>Electric Mining Rigs Mk II</> can mine Originium Ore, Amethyst Ore, and Ferrium Ore.

mainGoalDesc.cn: 开采7个矿点
mainGoalDesc.en: Mine 7 mining spots

dungeonDesc.cn: 反应池可进行固体和液体的混合生产。请将植物粉末和清水输送到反应池中以生产植物溶液。
dungeonDesc.en: Reactor Crucibles can react solid material with fluids to create solutions. Add powdered plants and Clean Water into the Reactor Crucible to produce plant solutions.

extraGoalDesc.cn: 只放置1台水泵
extraGoalDesc.en: Place 1 Fluid Pump

featureDesc.cn:
将锦草粉末和清水输入到<@bl.key>反应池</>中可生产锦草溶液。
使用<@bl.key>管道</>连接反应池和储液罐可以将反应池中的液体输送到储液罐中。记得在反应池中<@bl.key>设定</>要输出的液体。
将<@bl.key>空的瓶子</>拖到盛有液体的储液罐中可以获得<@bl.key>瓶装液体</>。
featureDesc.en:
Transport Jincao Powder and Clean Water into the <@bl.key>Reactor Crucible</> to produce Jincao Solution. 
Connect the Reactor Crucible to the Fluid Tank with <@bl.key>pipes</> to transport fluid products from the Reactor Crucible to the Fluid Tank. Remember to <@bl.key>set</> the desired fluid output at the Reactor Crucible. 
Drag <@bl.key>empty bottles</> to a filled Fluid Tank to <@bl.key>bottle the fluid</>.

mainGoalDesc.cn:
使用反应池生产锦草溶液
使用钢质瓶盛装锦草溶液到背包中
在储液罐中存储清水
mainGoalDesc.en:
Use the Reactor Crucible to produce Jincao Solution 
Fill a steel bottle with Jincao Solution and place in the Backpack 
Use the Fluid Tank to store Clean Water

dungeonDesc.cn: 反应池在扩增更多缓存区后可同时进行多个配方的生产。请改进当前生产线，减少反应池的使用数量。
dungeonDesc.en: Expand the Reactor Crucible cache to produce different solutions simultaneously. Improve the current production line to reduce the number of Reactor Crucibles needed.

extraGoalDesc.cn:
改进产线，恢复锦草软饮生产
改进产线，恢复芽针针剂生产
场地内反应池数量不超过3个
extraGoalDesc.en:
Improve the production line to produce Jincao Drink again 
Improve the production line to produce Yazhen Syringe [C] again 
Do not use more than 3 Reactor Crucibles in the area

featureDesc.cn:
<@bl.key>反应池</>在增扩更多缓存区后，可以支持多种配方<@bl.key>同时</>进行生产。
将清水、锦草粉末和芽针粉末输入到<@bl.key>反应池</>中可同时生产<@bl.key>锦草溶液</>和<@bl.key>芽针溶液</>。
featureDesc.en:
Expanding the <@bl.key>Reactor Crucible</> cache lets you <@bl.key>simultaneously</> produce different solutions. 
Move Clean Water, Jincao Powder, and Yazhen Powder into an expanded <@bl.key>Reactor Crucible</> to simultaneously produce <@bl.key>Jincao Solution</> and <@bl.key>Yazhen Solution</>.

mainGoalDesc.cn:
让反应池同时生产锦草溶液和芽针溶液
使用封装机生产锦草软饮
使用封装机生产芽针针剂
mainGoalDesc.en:
Use the Reactor Crucible to simultaneously produce Jincao Solution and Yazhen Solution 
Use the Packaging Unit to produce Jincao Drink 
Use the Packaging Unit to produce Yazhen Syringe [C]

dungeonDesc.cn: 请使用管道、水泵和给水器进行液体的转移运输。
dungeonDesc.en: Use pipes, Fluid Pumps, and Fluid Supply Units to transport various fluids.

extraGoalDesc.cn: 清理2个大水池里的垃圾
extraGoalDesc.en: Clear out the 2 large pools

featureDesc.cn:
使用<@bl.key>水泵</>可将液体从池子中抽出。
使用<@bl.key>给水器</>可以将液体倾倒到池子中。
使用<@bl.key>管道</>连接水泵和给水器可以进行液体的转移。
featureDesc.en:
Use <@bl.key>Fluid Pumps</> to remove fluids from pools. 
Use <@bl.key>Fluid Supply Units</> to pour fluids into the pool. 
Connect the Fluid Pump to the Fluid Supply Unit with <@bl.key>pipes</> to transport the fluids.

mainGoalDesc.cn: 清理小水池里的垃圾
mainGoalDesc.en: Clear out the small pool

dungeonDesc.cn: 请使用管道物流设备合理规划液体运输管线，完成复杂生产线的布局。
dungeonDesc.en: Use pipe logistics units to create a working pipeline and complete the complex production network.

extraGoalDesc.cn: 将清水转移到另一个池子
extraGoalDesc.en: Move Clean Water to another pool

featureDesc.cn:
<@bl.key>管道桥</>可使两条交叉的管道各自进行液体传输而互不影响。
<@bl.key>管道汇流器</>可以将多条管道中的液体汇聚到一条管道中。
featureDesc.en:
The <@bl.key>Pipe Bridge</> allows a pipeline to cross over another pipeline without interfering the fluid flows of both. 
The <@bl.key>Pipe Converger</> can merge fluid flows from multiple pipelines into a single pipeline.

mainGoalDesc.cn:
将预置的管道汇流器连接到储液罐
将两个池子的清水通过管道汇流器汇入储液罐
mainGoalDesc.en:
Connect the existing Pipe Converger to the Fluid Tank 
Use the Pipe Converger and move the Clean Water from both pools into the Fluid Tank

dungeonDesc.cn: 请使用种植机和采种机实现植物的循环生产和利用。
dungeonDesc.en: Use the Planting Unit and Seed-Picking Unit to create a self-sufficient plant production loop.

extraGoalDesc.cn:
场地内只放置1台采种机
让2台种植机同时生产荞花
extraGoalDesc.en:
Place only 1 Seed-Picking Unit in the area 
Produce Buckflowers with 2 Planting Units at the same time

featureDesc.cn:
将荞花放入<@bl.key>采种机</>可获得荞花种子。
将荞花种子放入<@bl.key>种植机</>可收获荞花。
使用一台采种机同时为两台种植机提供原料可提升生产效率。
featureDesc.en:
Place Buckflowers into the <@bl.key>Seed-Picking Unit</> to get Buckflower Seeds. 
Place Buckflower Seeds into the <@bl.key>Planting Unit</> to get Buckflower. 
1 Seed-Picking Unit can supply 2 Planting Units with seeds for optimal production.

mainGoalDesc.cn:
使用采种机生产荞花种子
使用种植机生产荞花
生产荞愈胶囊
mainGoalDesc.en:
Use the Seed-Picking Unit to produce Buckflower Seeds 
Use the Planting Unit to produce Buckflowers 
Produce Buck Capsule [C]

dungeonDesc.cn: 种植机的液体模式可进行武陵地区植物的种植。请使用管道分流器在水泵数量有限的情况下同时为多个设备供水。
dungeonDesc.en: Planting Unit can use Fluid Mode to grow Wuling plants. You have limited Fluid Pumps. Use Pipe Splitters to supply Clean Water to multiple facilities.

extraGoalDesc.cn:
使用种植机生产芽针
补齐产线，并在储液罐中存储芽针溶液
extraGoalDesc.en:
Use the Planting Unit to produce Yazhen 
Complete the production line and store Yazhen Solution in the Fluid Tank

featureDesc.cn:
种植机在液体模式下可以使用清水和锦草种子生产锦草。
使用<@bl.key>管道分流器</>可以用一台水泵同时为多个设备供水。
将锦草粉末和清水输入到<@bl.key>反应池</>中可生产锦草溶液。
将芽针粉末和清水输入到<@bl.key>反应池</>中可生产芽针溶液。
featureDesc.en:
In Fluid Mode, the Planting Unit can use Clean Water and Jincao Seed to produce Jincao plant. 
Use the <@bl.key>Pipe Splitter</> to supply multiple facilities with clean water with just 1 Fluid Pump. 
Transport Jincao Powder and Clean Water to the <@bl.key>Reactor Crucible</> to produce Jincao Solution. 
Transport Yazhen Powder and Clean Water to the <@bl.key>Reactor Crucible</> to produce Yazhen Solution.

mainGoalDesc.cn:
使用种植机生产锦草
使用管道分流器完善产线生产锦草软饮
mainGoalDesc.en:
Use the Planting Unit to produce Jincao 
Use the Pipe Splitter to complete the Jincao Drink production line

dungeonDesc.cn: 请使用热能池提升电网总发电功率，恢复集成工业系统中各设备的运转。
dungeonDesc.en: Use Thermal Banks to raise the power grid output and restore operations to the AIC facilities.

extraGoalDesc.cn: 放置更多热能池提升电网总功率
extraGoalDesc.en: Place more Thermal Banks to increase total power grid output.

featureDesc.cn:
源矿可以作为<@bl.key>热能池</>发电所需的原料。
<@bl.key>热能池</>所产生的电能可通过<@bl.key>供电桩</>获取并接入电网使用。
featureDesc.en:
The <@bl.key>Thermal Bank</> uses Originium Ore as fuel for power production. 
Connect <@bl.key>Thermal Banks</> to the power grid via <@bl.key>Electric Pylons</> to add their power output to the grid.

mainGoalDesc.cn:
使用热能池为集成工业系统供电
让产线恢复运转并生产低容谷地电池
mainGoalDesc.en:
Use Thermal Banks to generate power for the AIC 
Bring the production line back online and produce LC Valley Batteries

dungeonDesc.cn: 请使用集成工业系统搭建紫晶质瓶的自动化生产线，以提供制作荞愈胶囊所需的材料。
dungeonDesc.en: Use the AIC Factory to create an automated Amethyst Bottle production line to supply containers for making Buck Capsules [C].

extraGoalDesc.cn: 使用2台精炼炉为塑形机提供紫晶纤维
extraGoalDesc.en: Use 2 Refining Units to supply Amethyst Fiber to the Moulding Unit

featureDesc.cn:
将紫晶矿放入<@bl.key>精炼炉</>可加工获取紫晶纤维。
将紫晶纤维放入<@bl.key>塑形机</>中可产出紫晶质瓶。
可通过<@bl.key>简易制作</>，使用紫晶质瓶和荞花粉末制造<@bl.key>荞愈胶囊</>。
featureDesc.en:
Place Amethyst Ore in the <@bl.key>Refining Unit</> to produce Amethyst Fibers. 
Place Amethyst Fibers in the <@bl.key>Moulding Unit</> to produce Amethyst Bottles. 
Once you have Amethyst Bottles and Buckflower Powder, you can use <@bl.key>Crafting</> to make <@bl.key>Buck Capsule [C]</>.

mainGoalDesc.cn:
使用塑形机生产紫晶质瓶
通过简易制作生产荞愈胶囊
mainGoalDesc.en:
Use the Moulding Unit to produce Amethyst Bottles 
Use Crafting to produce Buck Capsule [C]

dungeonDesc.cn: 有限的取货口限制了生产线数量。集成工业系统现已引入分流器，可将单一传送带分流出最多三条传送带。
dungeonDesc.en: The number of production lines is limited by the number of output ports. The AIC Factory now has the Splitter to split a single output belt into 3.

extraGoalDesc.cn: 使用分流器为4台热能池提供源矿
extraGoalDesc.en: Use the Splitter to supply 4 Thermal Banks with Originium Ore

featureDesc.cn:
<@bl.key>分流器</>可将单一传送带分流出最多三条传送带进行运输。
<@bl.key>分流器</>有一个输入口和三个输出口，将输出产物的传送带连接至分流器的输入口，再从输出口连出传送带，即可实现分流。
featureDesc.en:
<@bl.key>Splitters</> can split 1 transport belt into 3 to supply more facilities. 
A <@bl.key>Splitter</> has 1 input and 3 outputs. Connect the input belt to the Splitter's input, then connect up to 3 output belts to achieve splitting.

mainGoalDesc.cn:
使用分流器将紫晶纤维分别输入粉碎机、配件机和塑形机
使用分流器为3台热能池提供源矿
mainGoalDesc.en:
Use the Splitter to supply Amethyst Fibers to a Shredding Unit, a Fitting Unit, and a Moulding Unit 
Use the Splitter to supply Originium Ore to 3 Thermal Banks

dungeonDesc.cn: 请使用管道、水泵和洒水机对田块进行自动浇灌。
dungeonDesc.en: Use pipes, Fluid Pumps, and Sprinklers to auto-irrigate the plots.

extraGoalDesc.cn: 制作1份锦素炒饭
extraGoalDesc.en: Craft 1 serving of Garden Fried Rice

featureDesc.cn:
<@bl.key>洒水机</>会在田块需要浇水时自动进行浇灌。
一台<@bl.key>洒水机</>可同时浇灌前方的多块田块。
featureDesc.en:
<@bl.key>Sprinklers</> auto-irrigate farm plots when they need water. 
A single <@bl.key>Sprinkler</> can irrigate multiple plots in front of it.

mainGoalDesc.cn:
使模拟琼叶参田块旁的洒水机工作
制作1份正本补元汤剂
mainGoalDesc.en:
Make the Sprinkler in front of the simulation Redjade Ginseng Plot operational 
Craft 1 serving of Fortifying Infusion

dungeonDesc.cn: 现需将一批源矿运回仓库。请完善电网建设，并使用协议储存箱的无线传输功能将源矿远程运回仓库。
dungeonDesc.en: You must move a batch of Originium Ore to the Depot. Complete the power grid and use the belt-free transfer of the Protocol Stash to transport the ore back to the depot.

extraGoalDesc.cn: 从便携源石矿机中收集更多源矿并输送回仓库。
extraGoalDesc.en: Collect Originium Ore from the Portable Originium Rig and transport them back to the Depot.

featureDesc.cn:
使用<@bl.key>供电桩</>为<@bl.key>协议储存箱</>供电后可启动无线传输功能。
<@bl.key>无线传输功能</>可将协议储存箱中存放的物品直接运回仓库。
<@bl.key>供电桩</>在接入电网后可为其周围特定范围内的设备提供电力。
从<@bl.key>中继器</>运输电力到<@bl.key>供电桩</>可将其接入电网。
featureDesc.en:
Use the <@bl.key>Electric Pylon</> to power the <@bl.key>Protocol Stash</> and activate its belt-free transfer feature. 
<@bl.key>Belt-free transfer</> lets the Stash transport its contents straight to the Depot. 
An <@bl.key>Electric Pylon</> connected to the power grid will supply power to facilities within range. 
Transmit power from the <@bl.key>Relay Tower</> to the <@bl.key>Electric Pylon</> to connect it into the power grid.

mainGoalDesc.cn: 通过协议储存箱的无线传输功能将1500份源矿送回仓库
mainGoalDesc.en: Move 1500 units of Originium Ore from the Protocol Stash to the Depot via belt-free transfer

dungeonDesc.cn: 集成工业系统现已引入研磨机，可配合砂叶粉末进一步压缩原料，来生产制造更高级的药品和装备。
dungeonDesc.en: The AIC Factory can now utilize the Grinding Unit that uses Sandleaf Powder to grind materials into ultra-fine compressible particles for making higher quality medicine and gear.

extraGoalDesc.cn: 挑战用更少的供电桩来维持运转
extraGoalDesc.en: Use as few Electric Pylons as possible and keep the production line running.

featureDesc.cn:
将<@bl.key>砂叶粉末</>和晶体外壳粉末放入<@bl.key>研磨机</>可生产<@bl.key>致密晶体粉末</>。
将致密晶体粉末放入<@bl.key>精炼炉</>可生产<@bl.key>密制晶体</>。
将<@bl.key>砂叶粉末</>和紫晶粉末放入<@bl.key>研磨机</>可生产<@bl.key>高晶粉末</>。
将高晶粉末放入<@bl.key>精炼炉</>可生产<@bl.key>高晶纤维</>。
featureDesc.en:
Place <@bl.key>Sandleaf Powder</> and Origocrust Powder in the <@bl.key>Grinding Unit</> to produce <@bl.key>Dense Origocrust Powder</>. 
Place Dense Origocrust Powder in the <@bl.key>Refining Unit</> to produce <@bl.key>Packed Origocrust</>. 
Place <@bl.key>Sandleaf Powder</> and Amethyst Powder in the <@bl.key>Grinding Unit</> to produce <@bl.key>Cryston Powder</>. 
Place Cryston Powder in the <@bl.key>Refining Unit</> to make <@bl.key>Cryston Fiber</>.

mainGoalDesc.cn: 生产高晶装备原件
mainGoalDesc.en: Produce Cryston Component

dungeonDesc.cn: 请使用装备原件机生产紫晶装备原件。
dungeonDesc.en: Use the Gearing Unit to produce Amethyst Components.

featureDesc.cn:
使用<@bl.key>装备原件机</>可生产装备原件。
使用<@bl.key>蓝图</>功能可以快速搭建产线。
featureDesc.en: Use the <@bl.key>Gearing Unit</> to produce gear components. Use the <@bl.key>blueprint</> feature to quickly construct production lines.

mainGoalDesc.cn:
使用装备原件机生产紫晶装备原件
使用蓝图让2个装备原件机同时生产紫晶装备原件
mainGoalDesc.en:
Use the Gearing Unit to produce Amethyst Components 
Use the blueprint to produce Amethyst Components with 2 Gearing Units simultaneously

dungeonDesc.cn: 天有洪炉是武陵地区独有的工业设备，可以生产息壤。请使用天有洪炉搭建息壤产线。
dungeonDesc.en: Forges of the Sky are Wuling-exclusive facilities that produce Xiranite. Use them to create a Xiranite production line.

featureDesc.cn: <@bl.key>天有洪炉</>可以生产<@bl.key>息壤</>，使用<@bl.key>蓝图</>功能可以更快地搭建<@bl.key>息壤</>产线。
featureDesc.en: <@bl.key>Forges of the Sky</> are facilities that produce <@bl.key>Xiranite</>. Use the <@bl.key>blueprint</> feature to quickly construct a <@bl.key>Xiranite</> production line.

mainGoalDesc.cn:
使用天有洪炉生产1份息壤
使用蓝图搭建1条息壤产线
mainGoalDesc.en:
Produce 1 unit of Xiranite with Forge of the Sky 
Use the blueprint to construct 1 more Xiranite production line

dungeonDesc.cn: <@ct.key>陈千语专精于击飞效果，能够快速叠加破防，还能对单体敌人造成大量伤害和失衡值。</>
dungeonDesc.en: <@ct.key>Chen Qianyu is a master in lifting enemies into mid-air. She can quickly build-up Vulnerability stacks and also deal massive DMG and Stagger to a single target.</>

dungeonDesc.cn: <@ct.key>大潘可以轻松地对敌人施加各类物理异常效果，同时还能通过连携技对敌人造成大量物理伤害。</>
dungeonDesc.en: <@ct.key>Da Pan can easily apply various Physical Statuses on enemies. His combo skill also deals massive Physical DMG.</>

dungeonDesc.cn: <@ct.key>阿列什是一名擅长控制敌人和技力恢复的先锋干员，他的战技能够立即冻结被寒冷附着的敌人，还能够通过连携技恢复大量技力。</>
dungeonDesc.en: <@ct.key>Alesh is a vanguard with crowd control and SP recovery abilities. His battle skill can immediately apply Solidification to enemies with Cryo Infliction, while his combo skill recovers plenty of SP.</>

dungeonDesc.cn: <@ct.key>管理员是能力全面的物理近卫干员，连携技能配合任意其他干员，并使用独一无二的源石技艺封印敌人。</>
dungeonDesc.en: <@ct.key>The Endministrator is an all-rounded Physical guard, with a combo skill that caters to other operators and unique Originium Arts for sealing the enemy.</>

dungeonDesc.cn: <@ct.key>弧光是电磁属性的先锋干员。她可以通过消耗敌人身上的导电状态，恢复大量技力，非常适合配合其他能造成电磁附着和导电的干员。</>
dungeonDesc.en: <@ct.key>Arclight is an electric vanguard. She can consume Electrification of enemies to recover massive SP, making her a perfect teammate for operators who can apply Electric Infliction or Electrification.</>

dungeonDesc.cn: <@ct.key>莱万汀是一名拥有强大群体输出能力的突击干员。她可以通过重击吸收附近敌人的灼热附着，触发强力战技和连携技，并使用终结技横扫大量敌人。</>
dungeonDesc.en: <@ct.key>Laevatain is a striker with outstanding mass DMG skills. Her Final Strikes can absorb Heat Inflictions from nearby enemies to trigger powerful battle skills and combo skills. She can also use her ultimate to carve and burn her way through mobs of enemies.</>

dungeonDesc.cn: 莱万汀是一名拥有强大群体输出能力的突击干员。她可以通过重击吸收附近敌人的灼热附着，触发强力战技和连携技，并使用终结技横扫大量敌人。
dungeonDesc.en: Laevatain is a striker with outstanding mass DMG skills. Her Final Strikes can absorb Heat Inflictions from nearby enemies to trigger powerful battle skills and combo skills. She can also use her ultimate to carve and burn her way through mobs of enemies.

dungeonDesc.cn: <@ct.key>别礼是一名通过叠加寒冷附着来进行输出的突击干员。她的战技能通过较少的技力，在重击中对敌人造成寒冷附着。她还能通过持续叠加寒冷附着层数，触发连携技和终结技，造成巨额寒冷伤害。</>
dungeonDesc.en: <@ct.key>Last Rite is a striker who deals DMG by stacking Cryo Inflictions. Her battle skill consumes little SP and help generate Final Strikes that apply Cryo Inflictions to enemies. Last Rite can also stack Cryo Inflictions to trigger combo skills and ultimates that deal massive Cryo DMG.</>

dungeonDesc.cn: <@ct.key>黎风拥有不错的输出能力，并且精于对敌人施加倒地效果。连携技提供的连击效果可以让其他干员更容易发挥。</>
dungeonDesc.en: <@ct.key>Lifeng is a good DMG dealer with a special focus on knocking down enemies. His combo skill gives a Link buff that increases the effectiveness of other operators.</>

dungeonDesc.cn: <@ct.key>佩丽卡是一名术师干员，能快速造成电磁附着和导电，为其他干员的发挥提供条件。</>
dungeonDesc.en: <@ct.key>Perlica is a caster who can effectively apply Electric Infliction and Electrification, opening up combat opportunities for other operators in the team.</>

dungeonDesc.cn: <@ct.key>骏卫是一名兼具物理输出和技力恢复能力的先锋干员。尽可能地消耗高层数的破防，能激发出他最大的能力。</>
dungeonDesc.en: <@ct.key>Pogranichnik is a vanguard with both Physical DMG dealing and SP recovery abilities. Try to consume multiple Vulnerability stacks to maximize the effects of his skills.</>

dungeonDesc.cn: <@ct.key>赛希可以通过战技回复主控干员的生命值，并通过终结技施加增幅来支援全体干员。</>
dungeonDesc.en: <@ct.key>Xaihi can use her battle skill to restore the HP of the controlled operator. Her ultimate can also grant Amp buffs to support the entire team.</>

dungeonDesc.cn:
这是一处内部情况未知的协议空间，认真探索，或许能够发现用于干员高阶培养的道具。
“我们行走在荒地，试图寻回因战争遗失的技术，寻回我们的起源。”
dungeonDesc.en:
A Protocol Space containing the unknown. Explore it properly and you might find some advanced operator progression items.
"We roam the wildlands to recover technology lost by war ... and pick up the trails of our true origins."

dungeonDesc.cn:
这是一处内部情况未知的协议空间，认真探索，或许能够发现用于干员高阶培养的道具。
“人类会丢失旧日的辉煌，但绝不会冷却沸腾的思想。”
dungeonDesc.en:
A Protocol Space containing the unknown. Explore it properly and you might find some advanced operator progression items.
"Past glories can be abandoned, but humanity will never let their raging ideas simmer down."

dungeonDesc.cn:
这是一处内部情况未知的协议空间，认真探索，或许能够发现用于干员高阶培养的道具。
“看吧，流于荒野的哀恸，庞大的、敌人的尸骸亦是我们的养料。”
dungeonDesc.en:
A Protocol Space containing the unknown. Explore it properly and you might find some advanced operator progression items.
"Witness the lamentations echoing across the barrens. The giant carcasses of our enemies will only nourish and strengthen us."

dungeonDesc.cn:
这是一处内部情况未知的协议空间，认真探索，或许能够发现用于干员高阶培养的道具。
“听吧，吹拂于冻土的呜咽，极光壁下，深埋已久的归途正等待我们找回。”
dungeonDesc.en:
A Protocol Space containing the unknown. Explore it properly and you might find some advanced operator progression items.
"Listen to the gentle whimpering that caress the permafrost. Our way home, long buried beneath the Aurora, still awaits our re-discovery."

dungeonDesc.cn:
这是一处内部情况未知的协议空间，认真探索，或许能够发现用于干员高阶培养的道具。
“我们的，人类的前路从未断绝。”
dungeonDesc.en:
A Protocol Space containing the unknown. Explore it properly and you might find some advanced operator progression items.
"Our path forward ... the path of humanity ... has never been severed."

dungeonDesc.cn:
<@ct.key>打断，打断至关重要。
在敌人的攻势亲在你们脸上之前，试试截断它，好吗？</>
dungeonDesc.en:
<@ct.key>Interrupt! Interrupt them at all costs!
Interrupt the enemies before their weapons kiss your face! Give this a try, okay?</>

dungeonDesc.cn:
<@ct.key>人类的防具、天使的外壳，这些都能挡住劈柴一样的鲁莽攻击。
灵活一点，让他们尝尝“猛击”。</>
dungeonDesc.en:
<@ct.key>Enemy shields and Aggeloi carapaces can effectively block frontal attacks. 
Stay on your feet, attack quickly, and Crush them.</>

dungeonDesc.cn:
<@ct.key>你们的攻击要像群岛的飓风一样迅速、狂暴！
别给敌人调整的机会，“破防”之后接上“击飞”，把他们控制住！</>
dungeonDesc.en:
<@ct.key>Become the archipelagic storm and strike with the speed and ferocity of a tempest! 
Throw the enemies off their feet. Make them vulnerable then lift them to the skies! Keep them helpless!</>

dungeonDesc.cn:
<@ct.key>你们的攻击要像侵蚀区的落石一样沉重、凶猛！
别给敌人调整的机会，“破防”之后接上“倒地”，把他们压制住！</>
dungeonDesc.en:
<@ct.key>Strike with the fearsome weight of Blight Zone boulders! 
Throw the enemies off their feet! Make them vulnerable then knock them to the ground! Keep them helpless!</>

dungeonDesc.cn:
<@ct.key>刀、剑、铳械、施术单元、防御装甲，源石技艺的痕迹无处不在。
活用它，试试“法术附着”和“法术爆发”。</>
dungeonDesc.en:
<@ct.key>Originium Arts have been employed in every form of weaponry and equipment: blades, swords, handcannons, Arts units, and armor suits. 
Wield the power of Arts Inflictions and Arts Bursts.</>

dungeonDesc.cn:
<@ct.key>火焰这种攻击方式，廉价、高效。
来，让你们的敌人身陷“燃烧”。</>
dungeonDesc.en:
<@ct.key>Heat is a cheap and effective form of energy.
Come, it's time to combust your enemies.</>

dungeonDesc.cn:
<@ct.key>僵化他们的思维，困缚他们的躯体。
来，让你们的敌人身陷“冻结”。</>
dungeonDesc.en:
<@ct.key>Freeze their minds and lock their physical forms in place.
Use cryogenic forces to solidify your enemies.</>

dungeonDesc.cn:
<@ct.key>让机械的血液也在人类体内流淌吧。
来，让你们的敌人身陷“导电”。</>
dungeonDesc.en:
<@ct.key>Let the electrons course through their veins.
See if you can electrify the enemies.</>

dungeonDesc.cn:
<@ct.key>想一想办法，让他们的防御装备像玉米片一样脆怎么样？
来，让你们的敌人身陷“腐蚀”。</>
dungeonDesc.en:
<@ct.key>Think of a way to weaken their defenses and make them as brittle as cornflakes.
Time to apply some corrosion.</>

dungeonDesc.cn:
<@ct.key>还不错，人多起来就能有一点“战场”氛围了。
闪避！闪避！躲开敌人的攻势！片叶莫沾身！</>
dungeonDesc.en:
<@ct.key>Good. The more the merrier! This is starting to feel like a proper "battlefield.
DODGE! Dodge the enemy attacks! Don't let them touch you!</>

dungeonDesc.cn:
<@ct.key>无论是岩石还是血肉，对攻势的忍耐都是有上限的。
积累对敌人的伤害，打破敌人的平衡！</>
dungeonDesc.en:
<@ct.key>It doesn't matter if they're rocks or flesh! Nothing can take a beating forever.
Keep damaging the enemy and stagger them!</>

dungeonDesc.cn:
<@ct.key>天使的外壳、源石技艺的产物，有时会比战车装甲还坚固。
灵活一点，让他们尝尝“碎甲”。</>
dungeonDesc.en:
<@ct.key>Aggelos carapace and products of the Originium Arts can sometimes be harder than tank armor.
Try to be flexible. Let them know how it feels to be breached.</>

dungeonDesc.cn: <@ct.key>狼卫擅长造成灼热附着和燃烧，同时还能使用战技消耗目标的燃烧或导电状态，造成大量伤害。</>
dungeonDesc.en: <@ct.key>Wulfgard is skilled in applying Heat Infliction and Combustion. His battle skills also consumes the target's Combustion or Electrification to deal massive DMG.</>

dungeonDesc.cn: <@ct.key>伊冯是一名通过暴击造成大量输出的干员。尽可能让她的技能施加冻结可以快速积攒终结技能量；施放终结技后，能获得强力的单体输出能力。</>
dungeonDesc.en: <@ct.key>Yvonne is a DMG dealer who leverages her critical hits. Try to apply Solidification with her skills to quickly gain Ultimate Energy. After casting her ultimate, Yvonne becomes a powerful single-target DMG dealer.</>

dungeonDesc.cn:
在这片荒野上，弥漫着仿佛永不消散的雪雾。耳边沉闷的轰隆声里夹杂着清脆的破碎声。
仔细听，好像还有……石头在摩擦金属？
dungeonDesc.en:
The snowy fog never seems to dissipate from these wildlands. Crisp sounds of shattering could be heard hidden within the low rumblings. 
Listen close. Did you hear ... stone grinding against metal?

featureDesc.cn: 敌人能力获得强化
featureDesc.en: Enemies are stronger

featureDesc.cn:
敌人能力获得强化
敌人的移动速度提升、失衡状态的持续时间减少
有敌人被击败后，剩余敌人更难被打断、不断提高攻击力并回复生命值
禁止使用战术物品和消耗品
featureDesc.en:
Enemies are stronger
Enemies move faster and recover from Staggered more quickly
When an enemy is defeated, the remaining enemies become harder to interrupt, and continuously gain ATK and HP restoration
Tacticals and consumables cannot be used

dungeonDesc.cn:
震耳的轰鸣带来了百年前的硝烟，但文明环带从未因天使的轰击而毁灭。
“可悲的是，险些让人类毁灭的不仅是天使。”
dungeonDesc.en:
The deafening blast brought embers of war from a century ago. Nevertheless, the Civilization Band was not destroyed by the Aggeloid bombardment. 
"It wasn't just the Aggeloi that brought humanity close to extinction. And that is the tragedy."

dungeonDesc.cn:
举目望去，巨大的机械残骸宣告着这里的过往。不远处，分解的物体重新聚拢，新生的个体发出撕裂大地的嚎叫。
砸向地面的天使，踏地的巨响，让大地开始颤抖。
dungeonDesc.en:
The giant machine wreckage in the distance heralded the great events of the past. Nearby, disassembled entities began to coalesce, creating newborn entities that belched with earth-rending howls. 
The land began to tremble as the Aggeloi slammed into the ground and waded their ponderous steps.

dungeonDesc.cn:
碾骨的战士将懦弱撕碎，举起斧与巨弩站于高台。击败他们吧，让旧日的苦难与今日的野心一并归于尘土。
“英雄？你如何能被称为英雄？”
dungeonDesc.en:
The Bonekrusher warriors eviscerated the weak and stood atop the platform with their axe and ballista raised. Defeat them and lay both ancient suffering and newfound ambition in the dust. 
"Hero? How did you earn this title?"

通信设备传出刺耳的杂音，无人机径直撞向地面，呢喃“赐福”与“复仇”的裂地者望了过来。
他们的身后，几个高大的身影出现在林立的巢雕之间。

The comm devices gave piercing screeches as drones crashed into the ground. The Landbreakers turned to look as they mumbled desires for "blessings" and "vengeance". 
Behind them stood tall shadowy figures amongst the forest of denstacks.

dungeonDesc.cn:
巨大的工厂，浓雾从管道里逸出，散发着刺鼻的气息。是谁想把秘密藏在这里？
“握好刀铳，装上盾牌，让牙兽吠吼！让烟雾沸腾！”

The massive factory belched thick, noxious exhaust from its pipes. Who is trying to hide their secrets here? 
"Draw your steel and raise those shields! Let howl the tuskbeasts of war! And heat up that haze!"
